title: Snap
description:
In these strong pieces of literary fiction, you are taken to the very depths of the human condition. From a young boxer, to a heart broken guitarist, this quick read will fascinate you while the text hums a rhythmic tempo. Showing good things come in small packages, Ceretto hammers the reader with powerful writing that will Snap you into attention.

From the authors website. Spread the word, this guy is awesome!
